articles.title: GCET Jammu holds innovation bootcamp to promote student entrepreneurship
articles.description: Excelsior Correspondent JAMMU, Nov 26: The Government College of Engineering and Technology (GCET) Jammu, in collaboration with DST iTBI-IIM Jammu, organised an Innovation Bootcamp titled “Prerna Se Udyamita Tak” to encourage student entrepreneurship and problem-solving. The programme brought together experts from IIM Jammu and local entrepreneurs to help students develop creative ideas and understand the basics of innovation and start-up building. A statement said that the bootcamp offered hands-on sessions on idea generation, innovation techniques, and early-stage business strategies. Students […]
